<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   All 19 members of the Senate Foreign Relations
Committee want President Bush to ask Soviet President Mikhail S.
Gorbachev to clarify the Soviet commitment to the treaty banning
medium-range nuclear-armed missiles.
