system disorders and other ailments, was examined by doctors at the
Mayo Clinic in Rochester, and a medical regimen was prescribed.
   Prison officials blamed her failure to adhere to the regimen for
her collapse in January.
   Her husband, former intelligence analyst Jonathan J. Pollard, is
serving a life sentence for giving Israel secret documents.
